window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Quickly overcome anxiety and worry with the 2020 updated version of the best seller by Michelle Galler.</b></p> <p>Dealing with worry, stress, panic, fear, negative thinking, anxiety and worry (to name just a few of the factors that can affect people these days) is never easy, but, fast relief is available.</p> <p>“…this is the only book I regularly recommend.” (Michael Patterson, author)</p> <p>Michelle Galler has produced a simple, easy-to-follow and unique guide to living a calmer and happier life, leaving you more capable of dealing with the situations we face everyday.</p> <p>“The realistic step-by-step formula is why this book stands out from others.” (<i>Los Angeles Today</i>, March 2020)</p> <p>Some of the topics covered in this book include:</p> <ul> <li>Quickly and easily overcome anxiety and stress</li> <li>Dealing with relationships - family, friends and romantic</li> <li>Steps to creating the future you want</li> <li>Clearing out the clutter and nonsense from your life</li> <li>Mindfulness - a simple guide for everyone to follow</li> <li>Looking after yourself</li> <li>Reframing negative and worrying thoughts</li> </ul> <p>And so much more!</p> <p>“More than any other book, this one strikes the perfect balance between helpful methods and a deep understanding of what anxiety and worry is.” (Steven Greene, author)</p>"; 
